		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have an nes copy of faxanadu and a famicom copy of faxanadu. Can i swap the internal chips to make the famicom version english?<br /><br />Are the mmc3a and b pcbs compatable for a swap? Anyone ever done this?<br /><br />Both games are pretty cheap and common, just wanting to know if this can be done or not.<br /><br />Thanks!

		

