		<td><b>Re: Prg and chr chips interchangable for nes and famicom?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Faxanadu is CHR-RAM so you don't even need to swap the CHR part, only PRG.<br /><br />You could use a regular EPROM though with a little bit of rewiring, instead of taking the mask ROM from another cartridge.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


